<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation" 
	      xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml">
<Paragraph Style="{DynamicResource HeaderParagraphStyle}">
Syncfusion Essential Pdf Viewer
</Paragraph>

<Paragraph>
Essential Pdf Viewer is a new control for viewing and printing PDF files as well as exporting them as images.
            It makes use of Essential PDF API to read files. It can be used in any WPF application. All basic features like texts, images, shapes etc. are supported and can be viewed in Pdf Viewer.
</Paragraph> 
<Paragraph>
<Figure HorizontalAnchor="PageRight" VerticalAnchor="PageTop" WrapDirection="Left">

<BlockUIContainer>
<Grid>
<StackPanel Orientation="Vertical">

<Border CornerRadius="5,5,0,0" Margin="0,5,0,5">
<TextBlock Margin="2,10,0,10" VerticalAlignment="Center" Style="{DynamicResource HeaderTextStyle}"> Featured Samples</TextBlock>
</Border>
<WrapPanel Margin="10">
<StackPanel Orientation="Vertical"  Margin="10">
<Button>
<Image Tag="Getting Started\Pdf Viewer Demo"  Cursor="Hand" HorizontalAlignment="Center" Source="Images\demo.png" Stretch="None" /></Button>
<TextBlock HorizontalAlignment="Center" Margin="5"> Pdf Viewer Demo </TextBlock>
</StackPanel>
<StackPanel Orientation="Vertical"  Margin="10">
<Button>
<Image Tag="Visual Styles\PDF Viewer Visual Styles"  Cursor="Hand" HorizontalAlignment="Center" Source="Images\demo.png" Stretch="None" /></Button>
<TextBlock HorizontalAlignment="Center" Margin="5"> PDF Viewer Visual Styles </TextBlock>
</StackPanel>
<StackPanel Orientation="Vertical"  Margin="10">
<Button>
<Image Tag="Toolbar Customization\Custom Toolbar"  Cursor="Hand" HorizontalAlignment="Center" Source="Images\toolbar.png" Stretch="None" /></Button>
<TextBlock HorizontalAlignment="Center" Margin="5"> Custom Toolbar </TextBlock>
</StackPanel>
<StackPanel Orientation="Vertical"  Margin="10">
<Button>
<Image Tag="Print\Silent Printing"  Cursor="Hand" HorizontalAlignment="Center" Source="Images\Print.png" Stretch="None" /></Button>
<TextBlock HorizontalAlignment="Center" Margin="5"> Silent Printing </TextBlock>
</StackPanel>
<StackPanel Orientation="Vertical"  Margin="10">
<Button>
<Image Tag="Multi Tabbed View\Multi Tabbed Viewer"  Cursor="Hand" HorizontalAlignment="Center" Source="Images\tab.png" Stretch="None" /></Button>
<TextBlock HorizontalAlignment="Center" Margin="5"> Multi Tabbed Viewer </TextBlock>
</StackPanel>
<StackPanel Orientation="Vertical"  Margin="10">
<Button>
<Image Tag="Export\Export as Image"  Cursor="Hand" HorizontalAlignment="Center" Source="Images\export.png" Stretch="None" /></Button>
<TextBlock HorizontalAlignment="Center" Margin="5"> Export as Image </TextBlock>
</StackPanel>
</WrapPanel>

</StackPanel>
</Grid>
</BlockUIContainer>
</Figure>

</Paragraph>





</FlowDocument>
